lled  <b>Christianna</b> , under the influence of the name   Anna ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Christiana Paynell was born about 1160, in Bampton, Devon, England, her father, Foulques Paynel of Bampton, was 42 and her mother, Lesceline de Subligny, was 32. She had at least 1 son with Milo (Miles) de Cogan. She died in 1211, in her hometown, at the age of 52."},"et":{"about 1160–1211":"umbes 1160–1211","1135–1216":"1135–1216","1148–1184":"1148–1184","1150–1215":"1150–1215","1150–Male":"1150–Surnud","1158–Male":"1158–Surnud","1160–1211":"1160–1211","1135–1183":"1135–1183","1164–1238":"1164–1238","1120–1182":"1120–1182","1130–1150":"1130–1150","about 1160":"umbes 1160","about 1182":"umbes 1182","1164":"1164","1120":"1120","1130":"1130","1184":"1184","1183":"1183","1150":"1150","1182":"1182","1160":"1160","1238":"1238","1216":"1216","1215":"1215","1148":"1148","1158":"1158","1135":"1135","1211":"1211","about 1155":"umbes 1155","Bampton, Devon, England":"Bampton, Devon, England","Cogan, Glamorgan, Wales":"Cogan, Glamorgan, Wales","Hambye, Manche, Basse-Normandie, France":"Hambye, Manche, Normandie, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"about 1160–1211":"noin 1160–1211","1135–1216":"1135–1216","1148–1184":"1148–1184","1150–1215":"1150–1215","1150–Male":"1150–Kuollut","1158–Male":"1158–Kuollut","1160–1211":"1160–1211","1135–1183":"1135–1183","1164–1238":"1164–1238","1120–1182":"1120–1182","1130–1150":"1130–1150","about 1160":"noin 1160","about 1182":"noin 1182","1164":"1164","1120":"1120","1130":"1130","1184":"1184","1183":"1183","1150":"1150","1182":"1182","1160":"1160","1238":"1238","1216":"1216","1215":"1215","1148":"1148","1158":"1158","1135":"1135","1211":"1211","about 1155":"noin 1155","Bampton, Devon, England":"Bampton, Devon, England","Cogan, Glamorgan, Wales":"Cogan, Glamorgan, Wales","Hambye, Manche, Basse-Normandie, France":"Hambye, Manche, Normandie, Ranska"},"fr":{"about 1160–1211":"environ 1160–1211","1135–1216":"1135–1216","1148–1184":"1148–1184","1150–1215":"1150